{"word":"G2648 - καταμανθάνω - katamanthánō - kat-am-an-than'-o - Consider","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταμανθάνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">katamanthánō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-am-an-than'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Consider</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கவனி"},{"paragraph":"to learn thoroughly examine carefully; to consider well"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G3129 - μανθάνω - manthánō - man-than'-o/3129\">G3129</a>; to <i>learn thoroughly</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>note carefully:</i> - consider.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2648/2648\">G2648</a>, <a href=\"#/G3100/3100\">G3100</a>, <a href=\"#/G3101/3101\">G3101</a>, <a href=\"#/G3102/3102\">G3102</a>, <a href=\"#/G3129/3129\">G3129</a>, <a href=\"#/G4827/4827\">G4827</a>"}]}